fields.name: Epitomi
fields.description: (n) epitome; A person or thing that is a perfect example of a particular quality or type.

fields.name: Ephoria
fields.description: (n) euphoria; A feeling or state of intense excitement and happiness.

fields.name: Elpida
fields.description: (n) hope; A feeling of expectation and desire for a particular thing to happen.

fields.name: Ethiki
fields.description: (n) ethic; A set of moral principles, especially ones relating to or affirming a specified group, field, or form of conduct.
